PassFab ToolKit 1.0.0.1 - SeuPirate

PassFab ToolKit - Recover or reset passwords for Windows, Word, Excel, PPT, ZIP, RAR, PDF, and more than 100 document types. Lost login password for your Windows PC or laptop? Windows password recovery tool in PassFab can easily recover or reset Administrator password, guest password, or Microsoft account password so that you can get into locked computer.

PassFab Toolkit offers all-round services for password and product key recovery. One installation can satisfy all your password needs on the computer.

100% Recovery Rate
100% recover your Windows password and product keys.
 
Easy to Use
All operations and process have been simplified. Even beginners can handle it.
 
Broad Compatibility
Work well on Windows 10/8.1/8/7/XP/Vista.

Support all formats of MS (.doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx,*ppt, *pptx, *pps, *ppsx), RAR, PDF and ZIP.
